GDP per capita in 1962

ec_gdp_pc_1962.Rd

Example dataset with countries and their gross domestic product divided by total population.

ec_gdp_pc_1962

Format

A data frame with 135 observations on the following 2 variables.

country

a character vector

value

a numeric vector

Source

The World Bank
